In this episode of _The Major Issues Podcast_, the hosts dive into the highly anticipated _Creature Commandos_, the first animated series in James Gunn’s new DCU. Join us as we break down the first season, examining the wild and eccentric characters that make up this unique team of misfits, as well as how it sets the tone for the future of the DC Universe. From the fascinating world-building to the unexpected blend of humor, action, and heart, we discuss what worked, what could have been better, and what we’re most excited for next. Whether you're a lifelong DC fan or just starting to explore this new era, we’ve got you covered on everything you need to know about _Creature Commandos_ and its place in the DCU's bold new direction!

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

